wiki.text:
'Totally Plc' is a publication company that has an international portfolio of
publications and online services that target the world's Jewish communities. It
is listed on London's Alternative Investment Market (ticker = TLY),<ref>[http://www.londonstockexchange.com/en-
gb/pricesnews/prices/system/detailedprices.htm?sym=GB0000414416GBGBXAIMI0041441-
TLY London Stock Exchange]</ref> has offices in London, Boston and Tel Aviv.

Totally owns and operates:<ref>[http://www.totallyplc.com/services/publishing/
Totally Plc: Services: Publishing<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
* Jewish News, serves London
* The Jewish Advocate, serves Greater Boston
* [http://TotallyJewish.com TotallyJewish.com]
